Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:06.06,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:06.06,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Song by Matsuhashi Miki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reasons and hints are all connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With these, the truth unravels.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Long time, no see, Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even idols can have problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kid with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.57,0:00:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is... Detective Conan!
