Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.67,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,The start of century.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.18,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,tashika na mono nakute
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.18,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Nothing can be considered certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:41.27,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,hitori ja nakenai yowasa hate myself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:41.27,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,I can't cry over my weaknesses, I can only hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:51.03,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,shinjiteru itami hikikae ni kono mune umetsukushite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:51.03,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Believing in this pain, my chest endures through the exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:59.83,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,ima utsutte iru futari ga eranda michi kuru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:59.83,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,The future that the two of us can be together is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:03.45,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,I think it's only my destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:03.45,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,I think it's only my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:06.83,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,hateshinai yami no mukou ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:06.83,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,On the other side of this persistent darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:13.17,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,dare mo shiru koto no nai ashita ga aru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:13.17,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,There's a tomorrow that has no time limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:18.18,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,oh yeah. You're going nowhere, It's only destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:18.18,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. You're going nowhere, It's only destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:21.47,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,ari no mama ni susunde
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:21.47,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Looking for that final resolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:28.81,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,ima kanjite iru you're in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:28.81,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,I can feel you now, you're in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:32.82,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,you're in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:32.82,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,You're in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:42.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L-O-V-E...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I love Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You keep watching the same show over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time you stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why does it matter? I'm bored anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you've got a lot of letters piling up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of them might be a job request.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll read them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just put them somewhere for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that he's bored, he just doesn't want to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see... There's bills, advertisements, more bills...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? There's a letter from Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a party invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're having an engagement party\Nat her friend's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Engagement?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her friend is getting married, and she wants\Nto meet the famous Detective Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going, right Da... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Engaged? Engaged? Engaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think he can hear you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:11.42,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Idol Star's Secret
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:11.42,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really, really, really excited\Nthat you invited me, Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to be invited to your friend's engagement party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no. I'm sorry it was on such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:26.18,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Okino Yoko (22)\NIdol
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After leaving us for the land of depression for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, who's your friend that's getting engaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll know when you see her, you\Nprobably know her very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:44.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you really did bring him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That famous detective, Mouri Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the guy who plays Detective Samonji?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:04.72,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Kenzaki Osamu (26)\NActor
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kenzaki Osamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you're Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s friend who's getting married?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm the groom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:17.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s friend is the one I'm marrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To actually bring the famous Detective Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll be happy, won't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I haven't told her yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to surprise her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go and see the surprised look on her face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like she's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought that everyone would be here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you came all the way to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't get hit by a celebrity that\Noften. It's another fun memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:19.00,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Kaoru Kusano (20)\NActress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:19.59,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's been someone stalking me. So when\NI saw a weird face through the peep hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least learn a person's face before inviting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you must be Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s friend\Nwho's marrying Kenzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:28.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:33.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our wedding will be next spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We aren't leaking it to the press yet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Kenzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is in\Nthat "Detective Samonji" show, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were thinking about watching tonight's\Nepisode to celebrate their engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:53.66,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Yuki Takeno (22)\NMulti-talented
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the golden couple of the millennium!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Takeno Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Again with the bright nails, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't these fake nails just so glamorous?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okino Yoko, Takeno Yuki and Kusano Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more, and we'd have all four!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How nice that would be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Terumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you came as well, Terumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:32.95,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Hoshino Terumi (23)\NActress
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but only because Yoko forced me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, well. Since all four Earth Ladies have reunited\Nafter such a long time, we should celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earth Ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Kusa" from "Kusano" represents the fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Takeno Yuki" represents the glaciers\Nat the top of mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:55.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Hoshi" from "Hoshino" represents the stars in the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and finally, "Okino Yoko" represents the water and oceans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:05.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, together, they're known as the Earth Ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:11.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four ladies representing four elements of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but Terumi and Kaoru had a fight, so we broke up.\NOut of all of us, the only person still singing is Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what's surprising is that the youngest\Namong us is the first to get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:31.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I always thought Terumi would be the first\Nto get married, but I guess I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Terumi. Didn't you used to like someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened? Did you ask him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget it, nothing happened between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rather than getting married, I want to keep\Nmy distance and appreciate from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:52.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, it's better to appreciate\Nthe person you are today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Terumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, who's the man with the kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, are you Kenzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Detective Samonji" is about to begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.47,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Atsushi Makuma (23)\NKaoru's Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to watch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take a bath while you guys watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the food that I've prepared will get cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, watching it together might—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up! When I say I'll pass, then I'll pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say such things to me, you depressing low-life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:34.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll never{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She hates watching herself on TV while around other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,J-Just as expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, are we really going through with that plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Definitely! That's why I invited you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, we'll wait for you in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge your clothes in the bathroom first, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:15.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! Those are the clothes the Earth\NLadies wore when they debuted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it! So when Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} gets out of the bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of us are going to sing\Nto celebrate their engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the outfits are a bit... embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:33.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you're fabulous! You're fabulous, Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're really gonna go through with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll go{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge next.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you hurry? I have to get{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ged too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's sign this card while we wait; from us to Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"May you have everlasting happiness."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're next, Terumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really should consider making up with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:20.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I have no choice, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} really want to meet Uncle Kogoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she even said so herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear her talking about that\Nstalker that's been watching her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wants him to catch the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, once she marries me, there won't be any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you signing the card?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, and everyone is writing something for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll go{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Sorry to hear about it", with a cigarette burn below it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:10.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if Terumi's mark is a cigarette burn, then mine is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Manager{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. Why\Ndon't you write something too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won't mind, even if you write complaints about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Did you not want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, I'm all done{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ging.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:55.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice, nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go get Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:04.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one watched my show's ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll play the song's intro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, let's wait for Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've called her several times, but she didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she fell asleep in the bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:42.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, Kenzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you should go check up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably just fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It leads directly to the doorstep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:56.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Kaoru, answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kenzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoru, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Comment: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:22.28,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Based off Manga\NVol 31 Files 5-7
Comment: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:22.28,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Original Air Date\NSeptember 3rd, 2001
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She still has a pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we hurry and get her to the hospital, she might make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's happening? Did somebody scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:14:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the victim is Kusano Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Age 20, floor 28, room 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But for a girl in her early 20s to be\Nliving in such a large apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably some rich kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard of the Earth Ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Earth Ladies"? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're coming in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I must have the wrong apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So many stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I'll ask one more time:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These three here, who were invited\Nto Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s engagement party,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,took turns{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ging their clothes outside the living\Nroom while Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ged in the following order:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Yuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and Terumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ging your clothes, Manager Makuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nwent to get her, but she did not respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that her fiance, Kenzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, went\Nover to the door and forced it open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that moment, you saw Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with\Nblood on her neck. Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, as if it were planned by the devil,\Nthis unfortunate case happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:34.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to say it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was invited here by Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}; it was only by{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:42.87,Dialogue Top,Note,0,0,0,,Translator's note: This is a Japanese pun, where Tamamata\Nmeans "By{\rHonorifics - Dialogue Top} chan{\r}ce" and Matamata means "Yet Again".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not Tamamata anymore, it's Matamata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:46.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, where is Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was taken to Haido Hospital to be treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't heard any news from Makuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nwho accompanied her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no point in waiting, I'll call the hospital\Nand ask them about her condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father is being treated for his diabetes\Nthere, so I know the number.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see... Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit who attacked Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, could it be one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's a possibility, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:30.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's often the case that whoever discovers\Nthe body is the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have any reason to murder her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that the boy with\Nthe glasses was there with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy is the one who told me to open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there was a trail of blood leading towards the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I opened the door, all of those were placed outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A raincoat, some old gloves, an empty\Neye-drop bottle, and a handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were all thrown outside the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We moved them inside before the ambulance came.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since these clothes are splattered with blood, they were\Nprobably worn by the killer at the time of the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are trace marks of a woman's\Nlipstick on the handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if this bottle had some sleeping drug in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he could have put our victim to sleep by placing the\Ndrug in the handkerchief before slicing her throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, who would do such a brutal thing to Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be the same person who's been playing\NDing Dong Ditch on Kaoru for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Ding Dong"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a prank where you ring a door bell and run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s case, it wasn't simply a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was always a letter left in front of the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'll come again." — "I'll keep coming again."\N— "I'll come even if I'm dead."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time he came, there was an even weirder\Nletter left behind, printed on white paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the reason Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} hit me when I rang the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the door locked at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there was a lot of people here, we weren't\Nworried and left the door unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we can summarize the events as follows:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stalker noticed that the door was unlocked,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and entered to face Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who\Nhad just gone toward the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, the stalker sedated her and sliced her throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he removed his raincoat and all the\Nother items found outside the apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:18:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Question all the residents of this apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it wasn't raining, and the murderer was wearing\Na raincoat, someone must have noticed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:09.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't think anyone would have noticed the murderer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he's a very careful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Careful?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally, when someone is wearing a bloody raincoat,\Nthey would step the blood dripping from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I looked, there was blood all over the\Nplace, but not one drop had been stepped on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that the murderer tried to run\Naway without stepping on the blood, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? But that's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he's such a careful person,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why didn't he notice the large number of shoes at the\Nentrance and know that a lot of people were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:56.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the culprit moved the raincoat extremely\Nslowly while walking towards the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:20:02.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,let the blood drip on the floor, and threw the coat outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trying to imply that the criminal had run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if that person was someone Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} knows,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he could've somehow convinced her to get out of the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once she got out, it wouldn't be hard to sedate\Nher and put her into a deep sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that the murderer is one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Officer{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Terumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The room we used to{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge our clothes is situated between\Nthe living room and the bathroom, which Kaoru was using.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't too hard to believe that one\Nof us could have silently killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever the case, Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did not try to murder her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We waited in front of the bathroom for her while she\Nwas{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ging her clothes, then returned together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'm safe, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was with the boy when we found Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who was nice enough to walk Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nto the bathroom could never have killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You walked her to the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:17.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:21.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you could have attacked her at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For now, I'd like to question each of you individually.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:31.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be searching for the most important thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dagger that slashed Kaoru's throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you can find it in this apartment or among our possessions,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then the murderer is definitely one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think an outsider would leave the\Nmurder weapon inside the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he wiped it clean, there would still be traces\Nof blood that forensics could find with luminol.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not something that one could easily hide, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this feeling I'm getting from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:21.98,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Aoi Aoi Kono Hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:21.98,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Song by Uehara Azumi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.36,0:22:33.87,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}shigekiteki na sekai o matte ita kedo kitto
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.36,0:22:33.87,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}I'm waiting for a world that's exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:40.12,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}me no mae ni aru subete ga taisetsu na mono nanda ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:40.12,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}But maybe everything before me is precious, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:52.60,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}ushinau koto kowagaru nante... watashitachi mada nani mo iretenai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:52.60,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}To be afraid of losing something... we haven't got anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:54.01,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}oh, yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:54.01,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Oh, yeah yeah yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:23:00.02,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}aoi aoi kono hoshi ni kagirinai mirai kasane
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:23:00.02,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}On this blue, blue world, limitless possible futures expand out before me.
