Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:05.27,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Can make me free, I don't want my heart to stop racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.27,0:23:06.44,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}oh, yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.27,0:23:06.44,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Oh, yeah yeah yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:12.49,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}kono kimochi maiagare sore to umi yaki tsukete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:12.49,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,{\fs22}This feeling starts to dance within me, burning the sky and boiling the seas.
